  "comment": "$$x^2\\log_{3^5}(4-x)\\leq \\log_3(x^2-8x+16)\\\\ 4-x>0~~~x<4\\\\ \\frac{x^2}{5}\\log_3(4-x)\\leq \\log_3{(x-4)}^{2}\\\\ \\frac{x^2}{5}\\log_3(4-x)\\leq 2\\log_3(x-4),т.к.~x<4\\\\ \\frac{x^2}{5}\\log_3(4-x)-2\\log_3(4-x)\\leq 0\\\\ \\log_3(4-x)(\\frac{x^2}{5}-2)\\leq 0\\\\ \\log_3(4-x)(x^2-10)\\leq 0\\\\ \\log_3(4-x)(x-\\sqrt{10})(x+\\sqrt{10})\\leq 0,т.к.~x<4\\\\ x\\in [-\\sqrt{10};3]\\cup [\\sqrt{10};4)$$\nОтвет: \\(x\\in [ -\\sqrt{10} ;3] \\ [\\sqrt{10} ;4)\\).",
